"evampi āpattañ­ña­bhāgi­yaṃ hoti leso ca upādinno, āpatti vācāya, vācāya "
"saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"thus using an unrelated offense as a pretext, he commits an offense "
"entailing suspension for each statement."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="45"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1670"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.2.22"
msgid "Bhikkhu pācittiyaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "A monk sees a second monk committing an offense entailing confession …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.2.23"
msgid "pāṭidesanīyaṃ …"
msgstr "an offense entailing acknowledgment …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.2.24"
msgid "dukkaṭaṃ …"
msgstr "an offense of wrong conduct …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.2.25"
msgid ""
"dubbhāsitaṃ ajjhāpajjanto diṭṭho hoti dubbhāsite dub­bhāsi­ta­diṭṭhi hoti … "
"pe …"
msgstr ""
"an offense of bad speech, and the first monk thinks it is an offense of bad "
"speech …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.2.26"
msgid "dubbhāsite saṃ­ghā­di­sesa­diṭṭhi hoti …"
msgstr "but the first monk thinks it is an offense entailing suspension …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.2.27"
msgid "thullac­caya­diṭṭhi hoti …"
msgstr "but the first monk thinks it is a serious offense …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.2.28"
msgid "pācit­ti­yadiṭ­ṭhi hoti …"
msgstr "but the first monk thinks it is an offense entailing confession …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.2.29"
msgid "pāṭi­de­sanīya­diṭṭhi hoti …"
msgstr "but the first monk thinks it is an offense entailing acknowledgment …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.2.30"
msgid "dukkaṭadiṭṭhi hoti."
msgstr "but the first monk thinks it is an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.2.31"
msgid "Tañce pārājikena codāpeti—"
msgstr "If he then has him accused of an offense entailing expulsion, saying,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.2.32"
msgid "“assamaṇosi, asakya­putti­yosi,"
msgstr "“You’re no longer an ascetic, not a son of the Sakyan;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.2.33"
msgid "natthi tayā saddhiṃ uposatho vā pavāraṇā vā saṃghakammaṃ vā”ti,"
msgstr ""
"you’re excluded from the observance-day ceremony, from the invitation "
"ceremony, from procedures of the Order,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.2.34"
msgid ""
"evampi āpattañ­ña­bhāgi­yaṃ hoti leso ca upādinno, āpatti vācāya, vācāya "
"saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"thus using an unrelated offense as a pretext, he commits an offense "
"entailing suspension for each statement."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.3.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Non-offenses"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="46"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.9.3.3"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1671"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.3.1"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr "There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.3.2"
msgid "tathāsaññī codeti vā codāpeti vā,"
msgstr ""
"if he accuses or causes someone to be accused in accordance with his own "
"perception;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.3.3"
msgid "ummattakassa,"
msgstr "if he is insane;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.3.4"
msgid "ādi­kammi­kas­sāti."
msgstr "if he is the first offender."

#. </p><hr><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="47"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1672"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss9:pts-cs3.3.5"
msgid "(Aññabhāgiya) Kiñci­lesa­sikkhā­padaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The ninth rule, the training rule on a (unrelated) pretext, is finished."

